videos.description: Kansas' Marcus Garrett gets the great block on defense and finds Ochai Agabaji for the fast-break dunk.
videos.headline: Kansas block leads to monster dunk

videos.description: Kansas and Texas commit consecutive turnovers leading to a mad dash for the ball.
videos.headline: Kansas, Texas scramble for the ball

videos.description: Texas' Jaxson Hayes lets the defender fly by, then throws it down for an easy two points.
videos.headline: Hayes shows his patience for the dunk
